<br>
Using Dalebs formula the delay is calculated at 18/(1+100%) or 18/2 ie. 9.  A 9/18 weapon at 100% haste therefore becomes a 9/9 weapon.<br>
<br>
The half haste idea would only work correctly on 100% haste though, as I say through coincidence.  The 21% haste on the FBSS gives rise to an improvement in delay of apporximtely 17% not 10.5%. <p>Tarrask, 51st Swifttail of Saryrn
